7\u5c0f\u968f\u9891\u7387\u53d8\u5316\u7684\u5185\u8054\u94fe\u63a5\u5217\u8868\u3002</Description><Description language-id="nl_NL">Termen weergeven als een gealigneerde lijst met links van verschillende lengte op basis van frequentie.</Description><Description language-id="fi_FI">N\u00e4yt\u00e4 termit inline-luettelona koko vaihdellen esiintymistaajuuden mukaan.</Description><Description language-id="fr_FR">Afficher les termes sous la forme d''une liste int\u00e9gr\u00e9e de liens dont les tailles varient en fonction des fr\u00e9quences.</Description><Description language-id="de_DE">Begriffe als eingebettete Linkliste mit unterschiedlichen Gr\u00f6\u00dfen auf Basis der H\u00e4ufigkeit anzeigen.</Description><Description language-id="hu_HU">Jelen\u00edtse meg a kifejez\u00e9seket hivatkoz\u00e1sok sork\u00f6zi list\u00e1jak\u00e9nt a gyakoris\u00e1gt\u00f3l f\u00fcgg\u0151en v\u00e1ltoz\u00f3 m\u00e9retben.</Description><Description language-id="ja_JP">\u7528\u8a9e\u3092\u983b\u5ea6\u306b\u5fdc\u3058\u3066\u30b5\u30a4\u30ba\u304c\u5909\u308f\u308b\u30a4\u30f3\u30e9\u30a4\u30f3\u5f62\u5f0f\u306e\u30ea\u30f3\u30af\u30ea\u30b9\u30c8\u3068\u3057\u3066\u8868\u793a\u3057\u307e\u3059\u3002</Description><Description language-id="pt_BR">Exibir termos como uma lista embutida de links com tamanhos variados baseados pela frequ\u00eancia.</Description><Description language-id="es_ES">Muestra t\u00e9rminos como una lista de enlaces en l\u00ednea con distintos tama\u00f1os basados en la frecuencia.</Description><Description language-id="sv_SE">Visa villkoren som en infogad lista med l\u00e4nkar med olika storlekar baserat p\u00e5 frekvens.</Description><Description language-id="zh_TW">\u5c07\u689d\u6b3e\u986f\u793a\u70ba\u9023\u7d50\u7684\u884c\u5167\u5217\u8868\uff0c\u9019\u4e9b\u9023\u7d50\u7684\u5927\u5c0f\u6839\u64da\u983b\u7387\u800c\u8b8a\u5316\u3002</Description></root>','ftl','<style ${nonceAttribute} type="text/css">\u000a\u0009.tag-cloud .facet-term {\u000a\u0009\u0009